OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1994FAn Afternoon on the Moon airs on
OL,7,FBBC One (CBBC). Presented by Zoe Ball
OL,8,Fand Gareth Jones. Marks the 25th
OL,9,Fanniversary of man's first steps on the
OL,10,Fmoon. Guests: Patrick Moore; Helen
OL,11,FSharman; the second man on the moon,
OL,12,FBuzz Aldrin; and making his only CBBC
OL,13,Fappearance, Gilbert the Alien from ITV.
