OL,6,CG2001FThe final episode of McCready
OL,7,Fand Daughter airs on BBC One. Starring
OL,8,FPatsy Palmer, Lorcan Cranitch and
OL,9,FBrendan Coyle. Drama. About an
OL,10,Festranged father and daughter who are
OL,11,Freunited in their work as private
OL,12,Finvestigators. The pilot aired on BBC
OL,13,FOne on 15th June 2000.
OL,14,
